data.description: back due to cold feet  buyers! Welcome to privacy & deeded Lake Murray access with a boat ramp! This home is situated on a spacious .42-acre cul-de-sac lot! Relax on the spacious wrap-around porch. You’ll appreciate the fenced in backyard space with an adorable playhouse, deeded Lake Murray access for swimming, boat ramp & putting in your kayak or other water toys & the community playground, soccer field & picnic area! Upon entering the front door you’ll love the enormous living room with a cozy gas fireplace, plantation shutters & beautiful hardwood floors! This leads to the spacious kitchen with granite countertops, bar & island, gas stove & a breakfast nook overlooking the backyard. Conveniently placed beside the kitchen, the formal dining area includes a stunning glass door & windows leading to the back deck & yard!! Off of the kitchen you’ll find a very spacious laundry room with storage cabinets & your washer/dryer can be gas or electric! Another entry/exit leads to the garage where cabinets line the walls! The owner’s suite is privately situated away from the living area & has stunning plantation style shutters with a bath that features a walk-in closet, double vanity, whirlpool tub, separate shower & separate water closet! Upstairs you’ll find 3 other bedrooms & a flex room that could be a nursery or office. Two bedrooms have their own private bath! Don’t forget the enormous FROG with easy attic access! Tons of storage & built-ins throughout!
